high_descs: Turn left and walk across the room to the counter.
Pick up the knife from behind the salt shaker.
Turn around and walk to the other counter.
Cut the fruit at the back of the counter.
Turn around and walk to the oven.
Place the knife standing up on the back left pan.
Turn around and walk to the counter.
Pick up a piece of fruit.
Turn around and carry the fruit to the oven.
Put the fruit in the pan with the knife.
Pick up the pan with the fruit and knife.
Turn left to the counter.
Set the pan down on the counter.
anns.task_desc: Put a piece of fruit into a pan on a counter.

high_descs: Turn and go to the counter by the stove.
Pick up the knife on the counter.
Turn around and go to the counter by the sink.
Slice the apple on the counter.
Turn around and go to the stove.
Put the knife in the pan on the stove.
Turn around and go to the counter by the stove.
Pick up a slice of apple on the counter.
Turn around and go to the stove.
Put the slice of apple in the pan on the stove.
Pick up the pan on the stove.
Turn left and go to the counter by the stove.
Put the pan on the counter by the stove.
anns.task_desc: Put a pan with an apple slice and knife

high_descs: Turn left and go to the counter to the right of the fridge.
Pick up the knife.
Turn around and go to the counter to the right of the sink.
Slice the tomato.
Turn around and go to the stove.
Put the knife on the pan on the stove.
Turn around and go back to the tomato.
Pick up a slice of tomato.
Return to the stove.
Put the tomato slice on the pan with the knife.
Pick up the stack.
Move slightly to the left.
Put the stack down on the counter.
anns.task_desc: Put a pan with a knife plus a slice of tomato on the counter next to the stove.

high_descs: Turn to the left, then to the right and go to the counter on the left between the fridge and stove.
Pick up the butter knife that is on the counter by the salt.
Turn around and go to the counter across the room to the right of the sink with the tomato on it.
Use the butter knife to cut the tomato into slices.
Turn around and head to the stove.
Put the butter knife in the pan on the back left burner.
Turn around and go back to the counter with the tomato on it.
Pick up a slice of the tomato from the counter.
Turn around and head back to the stove.
Put the tomato in the pan with the butter knife on the back left burner.
Pick up the pan that has the butter knife and tomato in it.
Turn to the left and go to the counter between the fridge and the stove.
Put the pan down on the counter.
anns.task_desc: Put a pan with a butter knife and tomato in it on a counter.
